                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " can be costly in terms of performance, particularly if the underlying tables are large and not properly indexed."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Indexes",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Ensuring that the columns used in joins and where clauses are indexed can significantly improve performance."
